{
    "maqras": [
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 1,
            "text": "When the Inevitable Event occurs"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 2,
            "text": "no one will deny its occurrence"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 3,
            "text": "Lowering some and raising others"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 4,
            "text": "When the earth is shaken violently"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "and the mountains are crushed and crumble"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "and become scattered dust"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "then you [human beings] will be divided into three separate groups"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "Those on the right. What of those on the right"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "And those on the left. What of those on the left"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "And those who are ahead upfront"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "they are the ones brought near"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 12,
            "text": "in the Gardens of Bliss"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 13,
            "text": "They are a large group of the earlier generations"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 14,
            "text": "and a few of later generations"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 15,
            "text": "They recline on luxurious woven couches"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "Reclining on them, facing each other"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 17,
            "text": "circulating among them will be ever youthful beings"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 18,
            "text": "with vessels, pitchers and a cup of a pure drink"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 19,
            "text": "causing no headache and no intoxication"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 20,
            "text": "There will be a selection of fruits"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 21,
            "text": "and any bird meat they desire"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 22,
            "text": "and Hoor Ein"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 23,
            "text": "like well-protected pearls"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 24,
            "text": "a reward for what they used to do"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 25,
            "text": "They will hear no idle or sinful talk there"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 26,
            "text": "only the greeting: \"Peace, peace"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 27,
            "text": "Those on the right, what of those on the right"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 28,
            "text": "[They will be] among thorns free lotus trees"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 29,
            "text": "and fruit-laden acacias"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 30,
            "text": "and extended shade"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 31,
            "text": "outpouring water"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 32,
            "text": "abundant fruits"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 33,
            "text": "neither withheld nor forbidden"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 34,
            "text": "on elevated daybeds"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 35,
            "text": "We have specially created them"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 36,
            "text": "originals"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 37,
            "text": "perfectly created and perfectly matching"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 38,
            "text": "For those of the right"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 39,
            "text": "a group of the earlier generation"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 40,
            "text": "and a group of the later generation"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 41,
            "text": "Those of the left, what of those on the left"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 42,
            "text": "[They will be] amidst scorching fire and scalding water"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 43,
            "text": "and a shade of black smoke"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 44,
            "text": "neither cool nor refreshing"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 45,
            "text": "They used to live luxuriously"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 46,
            "text": "but they persisted in the greatest offenses against God"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 47,
            "text": "And they used to say, \"When we're dead and turned to dust and bones, shall we then be resurrected"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 48,
            "text": "and our forefathers too"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 49,
            "text": "Say, \"The former and the later people"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 50,
            "text": "will all be gathered on a predetermined Day"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 51,
            "text": "Then you, you who are misguided and reject the truth"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 52,
            "text": "will be eating from trees of Zaqqum"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 53,
            "text": "You will be filling your bellies with it"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 54,
            "text": "drinking boiling water on top of it"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 55,
            "text": "drinking it like thirsty camels"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 56,
            "text": "That will be their welcome on Judgment Day"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 57,
            "text": "We created you, so why you do not believe"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 58,
            "text": "Have you seen the semen which you ejaculate"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 59,
            "text": "Is it you who creates it, or are We the Creator"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 60,
            "text": "We have decreed death among you, and nothing can stop Us"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 61,
            "text": "if We want to replace you and to recreate you in a way that you know nothing about"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 62,
            "text": "You have already known the first creation, so will you not remember"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 63,
            "text": "Have you seen what you cultivate"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 64,
            "text": "Is it you who makes it grow, or are We the grower"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 65,
            "text": "If We wish, We can turn it into ruins, and you would be left to wonder"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 66,
            "text": "[Saying], \"we are now in debt"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 67,
            "text": "Rather, We have been deprived"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 68,
            "text": "And have you seen the water that you drink"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 69,
            "text": "Is it you who sent it down from the clouds, or are We the Sender"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 70,
            "text": "If We wish, We can make it bitter, why then you are not grateful"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 71,
            "text": "And have you seen the fire that you kindle"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 72,
            "text": "Is it you who produced its tree, or are We the Producer"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 73,
            "text": "We have made it a reminder and provision for all who kindle it"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 56,
            "verse": 74,
            "text": "exalt, then, the glory of your Lord's Name; the Magnificent"
        }
    ]
}